      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "If you do choose to go this route (whether this is good design or not is another matter) and don&#39;t use constructor injection, make sure you also see <a href=\"http://stackoverflow.com/questions/5152686/self-injection-with-spring\">this question</a>"
