    "question_id" : 3423972,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can autowired BeanFactory inside the same class and do a</p>\n\n<p><code>getBean(YourClazz.class)</code></p>\n\n<p>It will automatically proxify your class and take into account your @Transactional or other aop annotation.</p>\n"
