    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The issue is related to how spring load classes and proxies. It will not work , untill you write your inner method / transaction in another class or go to other class and then again come to your class and then write the inner nested transcation method.</p>\n\n<p>To summarize, spring proxies does not allow the scenarios which you are facing. you have to write the 2nd transaction method in other class</p>\n"
